# Summary
This documentation page explains how to allocate traffic for experiments in Amplitude Experiment, including setting variant traffic percentages, targeting specific user segments, and configuring rollout percentages. It details how to define user segments based on cohorts or user properties, and provides options for handling internal users in experiments without skewing results.

